→ EMPTY_INPUT → Check if input is empty
→ VALIDATE_INPUT → Triggered by user input
→ INVALID_HEX_INPUT → Invalid hex input check
→ VALIDATE_ADDRESS → Check input address validity
        └── if invalid → INVALID_ADDRESS_INPUT
→ TEST_DUPLICATE_INPUT → Check if duplicate
        └── if duplicate → DUPLICATE_INPUT_ERROR
→ VALIDATE_EXISTS_ON_CHAIN → Check if exists on-chain
        ├── found → PREVIEW_CONTRACT_EXISTS_LOCALLY
        └── not found → PREVIEW_CONTRACT_NOT_FOUND_LOCALLY (terminal state)
→ PREVIEW_CONTRACT_EXISTS_LOCALLY → Prieview Exists Locally
→ CONTRACT_NOT_FOUND_ON_BLOCKCHAIN → Prieview Does not Exist Locally
→ VALIDATE_BALANCE → Check balance
        ├── if error → VALIDATE_BALANCE_ERROR (terminal state)
        └── if ok → VALID_INPUT
→ CLOSE_SELECT_INPUT → Promote and close
        └── set token in context, clear input → EMPTY_INPUT
